# Job Finder

- Next.js App Router under `src/app/`
- **UI: MUI only** — use `@mui/material` components, `ThemeRegistry` + `src/theme/theme.ts`. Do not add Tailwind or utility-class styling for layout/components.
- App Router cache: `@mui/material-nextjs/v16-appRouter` via `ThemeRegistry`
- **Database:** PostgreSQL ([docs/DATABASE.md](../../docs/DATABASE.md)); `PrismaClient` + `@prisma/adapter-pg` in `src/lib/prisma.ts` (no SQLite).
- Import `PrismaClient` from `@/generated/prisma/client` (generated output, not `@prisma/client`)
- **SaaS:** One build phase per task — check [docs/PLAN.md](../../docs/PLAN.md) and the matching [docs/phases/](../../docs/phases/) doc. Do not implement future phases.
- **Multi-tenant (Phase 7+):** Every query/mutation on `Application`, `StageEvent`, `Resume` must filter by `userId`. See [docs/SAAS.md](../../docs/SAAS.md).
- Keep changes minimal and focused
